"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-business-business-news-samsung-s-victory-selfies-at-paris-olympics-spark-sales-rise-for-foldable-phones-b1174632.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Business|Business News  News from The City, market updates plus comment and analysis from our business desk    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"victory selfies\\\" being captured by athletes on the podium at theParisOlympics have sparked a spike in sales of the foldable phone being used to take them, phone makerSamsungsaid.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The technology giant is a long-term Olympic partner, and for this year's Games is offering those on the podium the opportunity to take a selfie with their fellow medallists using its new foldable Galaxy Z Flip6 smartphone.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company said it saw a 23% spike in Flip6 sales on July 30, compared with an average day at the Olympics so far, with the day before marking Team GB's best day for podium placements at the Games so far, which Samsung said could have caused the spike in interest.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999735794856499, \"rank\": 2.6249239035368382e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9964326204311893, \"rank\": 0.0035801513080922463, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are also seeing a continued drive for foldables, with Samsung UK taking top spot for Galaxy Z Series sales in Europe  James Kitto, Samsung UK and Ireland  Last Monday saw the first flurry of medals forTeam GB, including gold in the team eventing and forTom Pidcockin the mountain biking, and silver forTom Daleyand Noah Williams in the men's 10m synchronised diving.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9964326204311893, \"rank\": 0.0035801513080922463, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9571578236584704, \"rank\": 0.044759782848739244, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9239392853439534, \"rank\": 0.08231394138878738, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}, {\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9571578236584704, \"rank\": 0.044759782848739244, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1272, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999947781584438, \"rank\": 5.150767460496291e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gigabyte\", \"score\": 0.9999996312368009, \"rank\": 3.665428175787319e-07, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gigabyte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gigabyte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as being used for the victory selfies on the podium, a special Olympic edition of the Z Flip6 has been given to all of the athletes taking part in the Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James Kitto, vice president and head of the mobile division at Samsung UK and Ireland, said the company was seeing a \\\"continued drive\\\" for foldable phones, and he revealed pre-order figures for a range of the firm's new phones and wearables - announced last month - were up on last year.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9239392853439534, \"rank\": 0.08231394138878738, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}, {\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9964326204311893, \"rank\": 0.0035801513080922463, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9571578236584704, \"rank\": 0.044759782848739244, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999947781584438, \"rank\": 5.150767460496291e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just a few short weeks ago we launched a new frontier of Galaxy AI devices, including the Galaxy Z Series of foldable smartphones, a new host of wearable offerings and our smallest form of innovation yet, in the Galaxy Ring,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999654392, \"rank\": 3.445978986587292e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have seen a positive start to sales captured within pre-order phase, which gives us the confidence our customers are as excited for these devices as we are.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For our new wearable offerings, which includes the Galaxy Watch Ultra, in the UK we are seeing an increase in demand year-on-year, up 37%; with health and wellness top of people's mind as we find ourselves mid-way through the summer of sports with the Olympic and Paralympic Games well under way.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2437, \"end\": 2442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraman\", \"score\": 0.932296172448496, \"rank\": 0.07261377167630982, \"text\": \"Ultra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraman\"}, {\"begin\": 2451, \"end\": 2453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9571578236584704, \"rank\": 0.044759782848739244, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Candidates for new series of The Apprentice revealed  Hottest hotel openings for 2026  Food supplier Greencore completes \\u00a31.2 billion Bakkavor takeover  Make 2026 the year of working smarter  \\\"Our wearables play an integral role in our ecosystem, historically driving both loyalty and attachment rate - over half of our smartphone users own more than one Samsung device, and our data tells us that those customers are also more likely to stay with us.\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 3122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comic_Relief_Does_The_Apprentice\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 8.047422690873577e-12, \"text\": \"The Apprentice\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comic_Relief_Does_The_Apprentice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comic_Relief_Does_The_Apprentice\"}, {\"begin\": 3026, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9964326204311893, \"rank\": 0.0035801513080922463, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are also seeing a continued drive for foldables, with Samsung UK taking top spot for Galaxy Z Series sales in Europe.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3182, \"end\": 3189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9964326204311893, \"rank\": 0.0035801513080922463, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 3190, \"end\": 3192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9571578236584704, \"rank\": 0.044759782848739244, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Galaxy Z Fold6 has jumped in popularity by 15%, which demonstrates a local demand for that larger screen experience, accelerated by the unique user cases of Galaxy AI designed specifically for Fold.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is also a positive story for Galaxy Z Flip6, where the 2024 Olympic Edition Z Flip6 can be found in the hands of nearly 17,000 athletes as part of Samsung's partnership with Olympic and Paralympic Games Paris 2024 contributing to a continued increase in consideration and purchase intent for our unique foldable smartphones.\\\"\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3602, \"end\": 3609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9964326204311893, \"rank\": 0.0035801513080922463, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\"